column2: "Oh, hello there. Do you have some kind of business with me?"
"If you have no business with me, then I need to get going. I don't want to lose this feeling."
"I think I've developed a knack for how to destroy Darkers."
"I wonder if this was given to me as a way to wipe out as many of them as possible."
"Anyone who gets in my way... I might as well destroy them too."
"I wonder why I never realized something this simple before...."
"She's dead because I didn't... I didn't realize this before..."
